      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">22.1003-2</ph> Geographical coverage of the Act.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1405e8" class="- topic/p ">The Service Contract Labor Standards statute applies to service contracts performed in the United States (see <xref href="22.1001.dita#FAR_22_1001"
                  base="i1096351"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">22.1001</xref>). The Service Contract Labor Standards statute does not apply to contracts performed outside the United States.</p>
      </conbody>
